P configuration limit from the <code class=\"code-grey\">UDesign Dashboard<\/code> page.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>UDesign works with any versions of PHP greater than 5.6+ and MySQL 5.0+, but these versions are already reached out the end of their life cycle. Using a low version of those maybe expose your site to security vulnerabilities. We recommend you should follow requirements for your server to use our UDesign. Using the latest [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[1],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/206"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=206"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/206\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":2697,"href":"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/206\/revisions\/2697"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=206"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=206"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=206"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"h